":2490502,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:40:33.000Z","msg":"怕北京 然之後奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b839c506828f0d488a52aeb8a8f10c316e1de5d9","tid":2490502,"uid":383301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:40:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://lih.kg/axLNKHV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/axLNKHV</a><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">支那人之鋒</code></pre><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2177544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2177544</a><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">館長並不反共\n也不反支那</code></pre><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">館長到處樹敵\n難免被暗殺\n這次是警告</code></pre><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2296813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2296813</a><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">    香港人玩TikTok\n    爛貨\n\n周庭利用tiktok賺錢</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZohghsio38D3ZREoSV2fbjBYV6pAYKtHLnrFhayEA26V?filename=ZBP31YS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZBP31YS.png&h=0f54143f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2474533\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2474533</a><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">    台灣人和了解台灣都無直接關係\n    正如香港人都未必了解香港\n\n所以呢？台鐵國營轉民營化與你無關</code></pre><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aAGDAtV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aAGDAtV</a><br />\n9up<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">黎智英的子女都在國外\n算是中國裸官</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2328902\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2328902</a><br />\n口號建國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSimonTW詞不達義之餘，亦從來唔解釋諗法。<br />\n<br />\n仲要喺眾志、肥佬黎出事落井下石、踩港，呢個人真係同路人？<br />\n<br />\n喺連登談論台鐵出軌嘅時候，又彈出嚟話唔關香港人事，仲惡過狗。<br />\n<br />\n出事就出Post做影印機洗底，難得仲有咁多人推Post、大叫港台友好，各位香港人係咪盲咗？</blockquote><br />\n台狗回應未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又話走屌你老母，原來台狗咁鍾意講大話㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa4731149a75e6228cadfbc5c0a80050da0da54","tid":2490502,"uid":383301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:43:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd05b76824e085c4cd709e16d2b861856c3824b","tid":2490502,"uid":281328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4d119bb8404134f979028d2452486f56d74d134","tid":2490502,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82b1c475c548eeee27e3c04adb2186c67196726e","tid":2490502,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:18:01.000Z","msg":"部份成員國擔心遭北京報復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:20:10.000Z","msg":"你愈怕 佢愈惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:44:06.000Z","msg":"你退一步，佢行前兩步<br />\n你企係到，佢行前一步<br />\n你行前一步，佢企係到<br />\n你行前兩步，佢靜靜雞退一步<br />\n<br />\n佢就係博你/兇你唔敢行前，甚至退一步"},{"pid":"bb9437ed6c2d3fdf77417f629e47856a60bbe622","tid":2490502,"uid":270220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:56:56.000Z","msg":"唔洗考慮，Do It<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50428af1c755b995471ab426b7ea702e4b6b523","tid":2490502,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb9437ed6c2d3fdf77417f629e47856a60bbe622","tid":2490502,"uid":270220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T